> define CatX: Category == with;
> 
> A: Join(CatX, CatA) == add;
> B: Join(CatX, CatB) == add;
> 
> X: CatX == if true then B else A;

Sorry, I meant

X: CatX == if true then A else A;

(no B anymore).

>> ---BEGIN aaa6.as
>> #include "aldor"
>> #include "aldorio"
>> macro I == MachineInteger;
